<br />\n<br />\n總之要帶出訊息呢樣野冇用！有弊冇利！ 仲要加d陰毛論 associated with DNA database、社會信用分，做個阻嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3df0a1e617d30e9c8ea34a1dec925e007428a6","tid":2155614,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7020864a3dfef751880e0c904c2789a0d3b386","tid":2155614,"uid":274363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4da865ccaee4968cb6c5f26fdb5dc8add40f8027","tid":2155614,"uid":274363,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:05:40.000Z","msg":"隔離post搬過嚟：<br />\n<br />\n請專家幫下口又好，靠大家文宣又好<br />\n煲大以下幾點，要同政府鬥快，唔好令藍絲/港豬被政府宣傳先入為主覺得係好野應該推行<br />\n<br />\n1. 有效性低：健康碼反映唔到一個人實時有冇受感染/病徵/傳染性<br />\n2. 成本問題：搞一搞要用幾耐時間、幾多公帑<br />\n3. 可靠性存漏洞：容易造假eg cap圖互傳有病扮冇病。例如你搭車司機邊會check係cap圖定真係個app兼且代表你本人<br />\n4. 對象普及性/針對性：上年紀人士(仲要係武肺高危群)可能唔識用，亦未必個個有智能電話<br />\n5. 造成依賴：可以預期一推行，健康碼反映冇病就等於免死金牌，唔再奉行有效既防疫措施eg量體溫、戴口罩、人群聚集、社交距離，當(1)應驗就仆街<br />\n<br />\n總之要帶出訊息呢樣野冇用！有弊冇利！ 仲要加d陰毛論 associated with DNA database、社會信用分，做個阻嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:09:20.000Z","msg":"煲大佢，製造輿論壓力，全民反推健康碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0920238d06e91ccb605d528270f5ac351b065578","tid":2155614,"uid":242283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T18:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24f0b1e1409272630da53e10d07b9c7d0d73c90","tid":2155614,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T01:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\